  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u00a0\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Federation will discuss and decide on the new Interim President: Sampanthan",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary Committee Chairman of the Tamil National Federation Sampanthan has said that the TNA will take a decision on the election of the new Interim President.",
        "Also, as of now, there are no clear disclosures about who is competing for the vacancy and what are their plans.",
        "Therefore, we have deep concerns about those issues and will take the final decision only after examining it as a group. He said that there are possibilities that the meeting will probably be held on the evening of 19th.",
        "At the same time, Sambandhan said that Ranil Wickremesinghe has been pressured by various parties to step down after assuming his duties as Acting President.",
        "Parties including protesters have criticized his inauguration. It is in this situation that the new presidential election is going to take place. Therefore, even then, blackmail should be carried out in accordance with the Constitution.",
        "He further said that the rule of law and political stability needs to be ensured as well as speedy action for economic recovery."
      ],
